verbose_text: ATG5 deficiency, for example, results in elevated IL-1 alpha secretion by macrophages, while inhibition of autophagy leads to promotion of IL-1 beta via reducing degradation by APCs and increases IL-23 secretion as a consequence, which can further promote Th17 mediated inflammatory responses.
